      "title": "No changes to fuel prices",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "There will be no changes to the fuel prices tonight, Power and Energy Minister Kanchana Wijesekera today said.",
        "However, he said that the next fuel price revision will be evaluated on September 15.",
        "According to amendments made to the fuel pricing formula, the fuel price revision is expected to take place on the 1st and the 15th of every month as per the fluctuation of crude oil prices in the global market. (Chaturanga Samarawickrama)"
      ],
